CĪON Investment Corporation

ICON Investments > CĪON Investment Corporation
CĪON Investment Corporation
CĪON Investment Corporation ("CĪON") is a non-traded business development company, or BDC, that primarily invests in the senior secured debt of U.S. middle market companies, which we define as companies with an annual EBITDA of $50 million or less.  CĪON's investment objective is to generate current income and, to a lesser extent, capital appreciation for its investors.  

To access information on the CĪON Investment Corporation website, please click here to be routed to www.cioninvestmentcorp.com.





